data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5 bedroom, 3 bath home in the Western Branch Reserve neighborhood. This spacious home offers a unique floor plan with unobstructed views through the house. Large windows allow for natural light to fill the space, showcasing a perfect blend of classic charm and modern amenities. A large 2-story foyer greets you upon entry and the open living room & dining room is nicely suited for entertaining guests. The kitchen boasts sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, a tech center, ample cabinet space and an extra large island with space for seating. The primary bedroom with a double door entry is a retreat on it's own, featuring cathedral ceilings, a private en-suite bathroom complete with a jetted tub, and walk-in closets. Three sizable secondary bedrooms and a laundry room are on the second floor as well. This is a must see! There's so much to love about this well appointed home. Schedule a tour before it's too late!
